al/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做咩...<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁點放你走"},{"pid":"8a5cd355f330dbe54f44f19bae0ec98b30d2e78c","tid":2325072,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T11:59:14.000Z","msg":"案件今（14日）在東區裁判法院開審，<span class=\"red\">被告並無律師代表</span>。拘捕警員供稱，目擊被告在隧道中搖晃手上噴漆，並在警誡下表示「Sorry Sir，我有悔意」。經審訊後，裁判官黃雅茵接納被告警誡下的口頭招認為呈堂證供，指當中不存在不自願性或不公平性，她認為被告當時明顯是準備將噴漆噴到牆上作破壞，故裁定罪名成立。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/33-%E6%AD%B2%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%99%B4%E6%BC%86-%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1-%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E8%AD%A6%E8%AA%A1%E4%B8%8B%E7%A8%B1-sorry-sir-%E6%88%91%E6%9C%89%E6%82%94%E6%84%8F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F33-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2599%25B4%25E6%25BC%2586-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25AA%25A1%25E4%25B8%258B%25E7%25A8%25B1-sorry-sir-%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2582%2594%25E6%2584%258F%2F&d=4UWfeJE2Id0Ic3Ynx8r7n8F4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=b5273418\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F33-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2599%25B4%25E6%25BC%2586-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25AA%25A1%25E4%25B8%258B%25E7%25A8%25B1-sorry-sir-%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2582%2594%25E6%2584%258F%2F&h=c9ea642d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/33-%E6%AD%B2%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%99%B4%E6%BC%86-%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1-%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E8%AD%A6%E8%AA%A1%E4%B8%8B%E7%A8%B1-sorry-sir-%E6%88%91%E6%9C%89%E6%82%94%E6%84%8F/</a>"},{"pid":"659466a03d157918e0e24b97b02678c98804ea2a","tid":2325072,"uid":115579